{"tid":1105662,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"原來蚊仔都會欺善怕惡？研究：成日被蚊咬全因為你太善良！","createTime":"2019-04-14T05:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T06:13:38.000Z","uid":215574,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa78f0f2528382388ece0594f6509c868a9a79b","tid":1105662,"uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"夏天即將到來，亦意味著惱人的蚊子又蓄勢待發，準備出動覓食。不知道大家身邊有沒有特別惹蚊的朋友？又或者自己正是那位可憐人？通常有惹蚊人士在場，其他人就可以逃過一劫。大家都認為惹蚊體質與血型有關，但就有研究指出，蚊子欺善怕惡，經常被蚊咬可能是因為你太善良！<br />\n<br />\n美國華盛頓大學進行研究，將蚊子放在充滿人類的氣味中。當牠們浸沐在人類的氣味中，研究人員就會以微小振動干擾牠們的叮咬行為，而這個振動強度與人類拍蚊時手臂造成的空氣振動相近，時間長達20分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201904/20190410184544_0_mosquito-2566773-960-720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201904%2F20190410184544_0_mosquito-2566773-960-720.jpg&h=a35b35c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n研究團隊發現，在接下來超過24小時的時間，蚊子都會避開這種氣味。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201904/20190410184555_0_mosquito-719613-960-720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201904%2F20190410184555_0_mosquito-719613-960-720.jpg&h=c4299cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據刊登在《Current Biology》（當代生物學）的一項研究顯示，蚊子具有學習及記憶能力。當你打算揮手拍死準備咬你的蚊仔時，牠會將你的氣味與自己差點一命嗚呼的經歷連接在一起，日後見到你就會避之則吉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201904/20190410184604_0_mosquito-871913-960-720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201904%2F20190410184604_0_mosquito-871913-960-720.jpg&h=f4a7596d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201904/20190410184612_0_mosquito-337182-960-720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201904%2F20190410184612_0_mosquito-337182-960-720.jpg&h=b566788e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n換言之，牠們會辨別到哪些人攻擊力較強，哪些人攻擊力較弱，所以蚊仔都是欺善怕惡的生物。如果你放任不管，就會一直被蚊攻擊。相反，如果一遇到蚊仔就積極出擊，就會令牠們放棄你這個目標。如果想擺脫惹蚊體質，大家下次可能就要放下慈悲之心，積極拍蚊啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/207158/%E6%9C%89%E7%88%B6%E8%94%AD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BE%9D%E4%BB%8D%E9%9D%A0%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%94%B1%E4%BD%8E%E5%81%9A%E8%B5%B7-%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%A7%E6%9E%97%E5%B3%AF%E5%BE%9E%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%B2%E5%88%B0%E5%B0%8F%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%BC%94%E8%97%9D%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F207158%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2588%25B6%25E8%2594%25AD%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BE%259D%25E4%25BB%258D%25E9%259D%25A0%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%2581%259A%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E5%259B%259E%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25B3%25AF%25E5%25BE%259E%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2594%25B2%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25BC%2594%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25B9%258B%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8kyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=f441fd69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/207158/%E6%9C%89%E7%88%B6%E8%94%AD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BE%9D%E4%BB%8D%E9%9D%A0%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%94%B1%E4%BD%8E%E5%81%9A%E8%B5%B7-%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%A7%E6%9E%97%E5%B3%AF%E5%BE%9E%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%B2%E5%88%B0%E5%B0%8F%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%BC%94%E8%97%9D%E4%B9%8B%E8%B7%AF</a>"},{"pid":"bc73ef3220ffd9c2a8fe57bf68042cb2e27c1182","tid":1105662,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:36:04.000Z","msg":"條link做乜撚"},{"pid":"768850dbf9618350ac32c4ee5a2ac0905b7029de","tid":1105662,"uid":215574,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc73ef3220ffd9c2a8fe57bf68042cb2e27c1182","tid":1105662,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T05:36:04.000Z","msg":"條link做乜撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https